Determine whether this social media post from Donald Trump contains a personal insult to Kamala Harris's intelligence. Simply return "yes" or "no".
content: RT @TeamTrumpPRESIDENT TRUMP: If Kamala wins, you will have Mass Amnesty and citizenship for all the Biden-Harris illegals—if I win, you will have the largest deportation operation in American History, starting at noon on Inauguration Day 2025.
